Class SheetEvent.RowsAdded

public static class SheetEvent.RowsAdded extends Event.AbstractEvent<Sheet> implements SheetEvent
Event representing the addition of rows to a sheet.

Extends AbstractEvent<Sheet> and implements SheetEvent. This event is triggered when one or more rows are added to the sheet.

The event contains the indices of the first and last row that were added (inclusive).
